743	## 2. Anatomy
744	
745	```text
746	Carousel
747	├── Root              <section>  role="region" aria-roledescription="carousel"
748	│   ├── PrevTrigger   <button>   "Previous slide"
749	│   ├── Viewport      <div>      overflow:hidden, touch-action
750	│   │   └── ItemGroup <div>      aria-live="off|polite"
751	│   │       └── Item  (×N) <div> role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"
752	│   ├── NextTrigger   <button>   "Next slide"
753	│   ├── IndicatorGroup <div>     role="tablist"
754	│   │   └── Indicator (×N) <button> role="tab" aria-selected
755	│   ├── AutoPlayTrigger <button> aria-pressed
756	│   ├── AutoPlayIndicator <div> aria-hidden="true" data-ars-state
757	│   └── ProgressText <div>  aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"
758	```
759	
760	| Part              | Element     | Key Attributes                                          |
761	| ----------------- | ----------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
762	| Root              | `<section>` | `role="region"`, `aria-roledescription="carousel"`      |
763	| Viewport          | `<div>`     | `overflow:hidden`, `touch-action`                       |
764	| ItemGroup         | `<div>`     | `aria-live="off\|polite"`                               |
765	| Item              | `<div>`     | `role="group"`, `aria-roledescription="slide"`, `inert` |
766	| PrevTrigger       | `<button>`  | `aria-disabled` when at boundary                        |
767	| NextTrigger       | `<button>`  | `aria-disabled` when at boundary                        |
768	| IndicatorGroup    | `<div>`     | `role="tablist"`                                        |
769	| Indicator         | `<button>`  | `role="tab"`, `aria-selected`                           |
770	| AutoPlayTrigger   | `<button>`  | `aria-pressed`                                          |
771	| AutoPlayIndicator | `<div>`     | `aria-hidden="true"`, `data-ars-state`                  |
772	| ProgressText      | `<div>`     | `aria-live="polite"`, `aria-atomic="true"`              |
773	
774	## 3. Accessibility
775	
776	### 3.1 ARIA Roles, States, and Properties
777	
778	The carousel follows the [WAI-ARIA Carousel Pattern](https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/carousel/).
779	
780	| Element           | Attribute              | Value                                            |
781	| ----------------- | ---------------------- | ------------------------------------------------ |
782	| Root (`section`)  | `role`                 | `"region"`                                       |
783	| Root              | `aria-roledescription` | `"carousel"`                                     |
784	| Item              | `role`                 | `"group"`                                        |
785	| Item              | `aria-roledescription` | `"slide"`                                        |
786	| Item (hidden)     | `aria-hidden`          | `"true"` + `inert`                               |
787	| IndicatorGroup    | `role`                 | `"tablist"`                                      |
788	| Indicator         | `role`                 | `"tab"`                                          |
789	| Indicator         | `aria-selected`        | `"true"` for current slide                       |
790	| ItemGroup         | `aria-live`            | `"off"` during auto-play, `"polite"` when paused |
791	| AutoPlayIndicator | `aria-hidden`          | `"true"` (purely decorative visual feedback)     |
792	
793	### 3.2 Keyboard Interaction
794	
795	| Key                           | Behaviour                     |
796	| ----------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
797	| `ArrowRight` (horizontal LTR) | Next slide                    |
798	| `ArrowLeft` (horizontal LTR)  | Previous slide                |
799	| `ArrowDown` (vertical)        | Next slide                    |
800	| `ArrowUp` (vertical)          | Previous slide                |
801	| `Home`                        | First slide                   |
802	| `End`                         | Last slide                    |
803	| `Tab`                         | Move focus into slide content |
804	
805	RTL: Arrow keys reverse per `03-accessibility.md` §4.1.
806	
807	### 3.3 Screen Reader Announcements
808	
809	- `aria-live` on `ItemGroup` is `"off"` during auto-play to prevent disruptive announcements, and `"polite"` when paused or stopped.
810	- Auto-play MUST pause on hover (`mouseenter`) and on focus within the carousel (`focusin`). Resumes on `mouseleave` / `focusout` unless `stop_on_interaction` triggered.
811	- Non-current slides receive both `aria-hidden="true"` and `inert`, ensuring they are invisible to assistive technology.
812	
813	## 4. Internationalization
814	
815	### 4.1 Messages
816	
817	```rust
818	#[derive(Clone, Debug)]
819	pub struct Messages {
820	    pub carousel_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
821	    pub role_description: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
822	    pub slide_role_description: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
823	    pub slide_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(usize, usize, &Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
824	    pub prev_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
825	    pub next_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
826	    pub pause_auto_play_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
827	    pub start_auto_play_label: MessageFn<dyn Fn(&Locale) -> String + Send + Sync>,
828	}
829	
830	impl Default for Messages {
831	    fn default() -> Self {
832	        Self {
833	            carousel_label: MessageFn::static_str("Carousel"),
834	            role_description: MessageFn::static_str("carousel"),
835	            slide_role_description: MessageFn::static_str("slide"),
836	            slide_label: MessageFn::new(|index, total, _locale| format!("Slide {index} of {total}")),
837	            prev_label: MessageFn::static_str("Previous slide"),
838	            next_label: MessageFn::static_str("Next slide"),
839	            pause_auto_play_label: MessageFn::static_str("Pause automatic slide show"),
840	            start_auto_play_label: MessageFn::static_str("Start automatic slide show"),
841	        }
842	    }
843	}
844	
845	impl ComponentMessages for Messages {}
846	```
847	
848	RTL: `on_root_keydown()` reverses `ArrowRight`/`ArrowLeft` when `ctx.is_rtl` is `true`. `PrevTrigger` and `NextTrigger` icons swap visually but semantic labels remain "Previous" / "Next". The slide track is ordered left-to-right in the DOM; CSS `direction: rtl` handles visual reversal.
849	
850	## 5. Library Parity
851	
852	> Compared against: Ark UI (`Carousel`).
853	
854	### 5.1 Props
855	
856	| Feature             | ars-ui                        | Ark UI                           | Notes                                             |
857	| ------------------- | ----------------------------- | -------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
858	| Current slide       | `index` (Bindable)            | `page` / `defaultPage`           | Same concept                                      |
859	| Slide count         | `slide_count`                 | `slideCount`                     | Same                                              |
860	| Loop                | `loop_nav`                    | `loop`                           | Same                                              |
861	| Auto-play           | `auto_play` (AutoPlayOptions) | `autoplay` (boolean or {delay})  | ars-ui richer config                              |
862	| Slides per view     | `slides_per_view`             | `slidesPerPage`                  | Same concept                                      |
863	| Slides per move     | `slides_per_move`             | `slidesPerMove`                  | Adopted from Ark UI                               |
864	| Spacing             | `spacing`                     | `spacing`                        | Same                                              |
865	| Orientation         | `orientation`                 | `orientation`                    | Same                                              |
866	| Alignment           | `align` (SlideAlignment)      | Item-level `snapAlign`           | ars-ui at root, Ark per-item                      |
867	| Swipe threshold     | `swipe_threshold`             | --                               | ars-ui addition                                   |
868	| Transition duration | `transition_duration`         | --                               | ars-ui addition                                   |
869	| RTL                 | `is_rtl`                      | --                               | ars-ui addition                                   |
870	| Mouse drag          | Always enabled                | `allowMouseDrag`                 | ars-ui always supports drag                       |
871	| In-view threshold   | --                            | `inViewThreshold`                | Partial visibility detection; not adopted (niche) |
872	| Snap type           | --                            | `snapType` (proximity/mandatory) | CSS scroll-snap concern; not adopted              |
873	| Padding             | --                            | `padding`                        | CSS concern; consumer can set padding directly    |
874	
875	**Gaps:** None critical. `inViewThreshold`, `snapType`, and `padding` are CSS-level concerns or niche features not adopted.
876	
877	### 5.2 Anatomy
878	
879	| Part              | ars-ui              | Ark UI              | Notes                                          |
880	| ----------------- | ------------------- | ------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
881	| Root              | `Root`              | `Root`              | --                                             |
882	| Viewport          | `Viewport`          | --                  | ars-ui separates viewport from root            |
883	| ItemGroup         | `ItemGroup`         | `ItemGroup`         | --                                             |
884	| Item              | `Item`              | `Item`              | --                                             |
885	| PrevTrigger       | `PrevTrigger`       | `PrevTrigger`       | --                                             |
886	| NextTrigger       | `NextTrigger`       | `NextTrigger`       | --                                             |
887	| IndicatorGroup    | `IndicatorGroup`    | `IndicatorGroup`    | --                                             |
888	| Indicator         | `Indicator`         | `Indicator`         | --                                             |
889	| AutoPlayTrigger   | `AutoPlayTrigger`   | `AutoplayTrigger`   | --                                             |
890	| AutoPlayIndicator | `AutoPlayIndicator` | `AutoplayIndicator` | --                                             |
891	| ProgressText      | `ProgressText`      | `ProgressText`      | Adopted from Ark UI                            |
892	| Control           | --                  | `Control`           | Wrapper for prev/next; consumer layout concern |
893	
894	**Gaps:** None. `Control` is a grouping wrapper the consumer can create.
895	
896	### 5.3 Events
897	
898	| Callback        | ars-ui                    | Ark UI                   | Notes                             |
899	| --------------- | ------------------------- | ------------------------ | --------------------------------- |
900	| Page change     | `Bindable` change         | `onPageChange`           | Handled via Bindable notification |
901	| Autoplay status | State machine transitions | `onAutoplayStatusChange` | Observable via state              |
902	| Drag status     | State machine transitions | `onDragStatusChange`     | Observable via state              |
903	
904	**Gaps:** None. ars-ui uses state machine transitions instead of explicit callbacks.
905	
906	### 5.4 Features
907	
908	| Feature                     | ars-ui | Ark UI |
909	| --------------------------- | ------ | ------ |
910	| Auto-play with pause/resume | Yes    | Yes    |
911	| Looping                     | Yes    | Yes    |
912	| Pointer/touch drag          | Yes    | Yes    |
913	| Keyboard navigation         | Yes    | Yes    |
914	| Dot indicators              | Yes    | Yes    |
915	| Multi-slide view            | Yes    | Yes    |
916	| Multi-slide advance         | Yes    | Yes    |
917	| Progress text               | Yes    | Yes    |
918	| RTL support                 | Yes    | --     |
919	| Momentum-based swipe        | Yes    | --     |
920	
921	**Gaps:** None.
922	
923	### 5.5 Summary
924	
925	- **Overall:** Full parity.
926	- **Divergences:** ars-ui uses `AutoPlayOptions` struct instead of Ark's boolean-or-object; ars-ui includes momentum-based swipe detection; ars-ui has explicit `Viewport` part that Ark folds into Root.
927	- **Recommended additions:** None.
